  "title": "B2B Sales Associate | Fun & Dynamic Environment!",
  "description": "<p><strong>Join us today – Where Sales Meets Fun!</strong></p><p>Are you a people person who loves engaging with customers? Do you thrive in a fast-paced environment and want to grow in a vibrant team? We are looking for enthusiastic <strong>B2B Sales Associate</strong> to join our squad!</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></h3><ul><li>Assist customers with product inquiries & provide excellent service</li><li>Support daily sales operations & maintain a well-presented store</li><li>Promote products & help customers find what they need</li><li>Work closely with a fun & supportive team</li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></h3><p>✔️ Outgoing, friendly & great at communication<br />✔️ Passion for retail, customer service & sales<br />✔️ No experience? No worries! Training is provided<br />✔️ A team player with a positive attitude</p><h3><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h3><p>✨ Fun & energetic work culture – No boring office vibes!<br />✨ Career progression – We reward hard work & promote from within!<br />✨ Performance bonuses<br />✨ Fun team events & incentives 🎉</p><p>📩 <strong>Ready to start?</strong> Apply now ~</p><p>🚀 <strong>Join US & let’s make sales fun together!</strong></p>",
